<section id="framework-approach">
    <div>
        <div class="row">
           <div class="approach-header">
            <center><h3><b>Investing Framework Approach:</b></h3></center>
           </div>
           <div>
            <center>
                <br>
                <h4 id="h4-class" style="font-size: 15px;">
                    This investing framework outlines a disciplined and patient
                    approach to investing. Here's breakdown of each phase with example:
                </h4>
                <br>
            </center>
           </div>
           <div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-2">
                            <div><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-circle-check Investment-famework fa-2x" style="color: #0047AB;"></i></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-10">
                            <div class="dic-color" ><h4>Phase 1: Invest</h4></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">
                            <br>
                            <div class="content-class">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                        For example you invest $200 monthly via Systematic Investment Plan (SIP) into ABC stock.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        Continue for 2 years or until the investment reaches $5,000.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        Let's assume our buying avarage price $100.
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-2">
                            <div><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-circle-check Investment-famework fa-2x" style="color: #1ff967;"></i></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-10">
                            <div class="dic-color-2" ><h4>Phase 2: Wait & Grow</h4></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">
                            <br>
                            <div class="content-class">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                        Waits for the price to double ( or ideally
                                        triple/quadruple), may take many months to years.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        Meanwhile you can monitor fundamentals to anticipate potential growth.
                                    </li>
                                    
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-2">
                            <div><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-circle-check Investment-famework fa-2x" style="color: #1ff967;"></i></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-10">
                            <div class="dic-color-2" ><h4>Phase 3: Cash Out & Free Your Investments</h4></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">
                            <br>
                            <div class="content-class">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                        For instance when ABC stock reaches $300(3x initial investment),
                                        cash out the original $5,000.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        Leaves the remaining $10,000 invested in ABC stock for the long term.
                                        Now that's become your free investment.
                                    </li>
                                    
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-2">
                            <div><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-circle-check Investment-famework fa-2x" style="color: #0047AB;"></i></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-10">
                            <div class="dic-color" ><h4>Phase 4: Spread Your Wings</h4></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">
                            <br>
                            <div class="content-class">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                       Reinvest the cashed-out $5000 into at least 4+ other
                                       promising stocks via SIP.
                                    </li>
                                    
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
